These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, thai, chinese, nigerian, brazilian, polish, dutch
There 7 different types of food: cherry, carrot, pumpkin, artichoke, cucumber, corn, garlic
City: liverpool, london, boston, nizza, hamburg, miami, berlin
7 different pets are kept: mouse, frog, chinchilla, hamster, ferret, guinea-pig, dog
 1. the argentine is on the left of the dutch##1
 2. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 5. the person eating garlic is on the far left##1
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 7. the person eating carrot is on the right of the nigerian##1
 8. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 9. the person eating pumpkin is on the far right##1
10. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
11. the polish is in the middle##1
12. the chinese is on the far left##1
13. the person eating cucumber is in the middle##1
14. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
15. the owner of the dog is on the left of the argentine##1
16. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
17. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
18. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
19. the owner of the chinchilla is in the middle##1
20. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the thai##1
21. the person eating carrot is on the right of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |    5     |     6      |       7       |
| Nationality      | chinese    | argentine     | dutch  | polish   | nigerian | brazilian      | thai          |
| Food   | garlic    | artichoke   | corn  | cucumber       | cherry  | carrot      | pumpkin     |
| City         | liverpool | london | hamburg | miami | boston   | nizza     | berlin |
| Pet     | dog      | guinea-pig   | mouse   | chinchilla  | hamster  | ferret | frog       |

