 2. the pakistani is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 3. the vegafina-smoker is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1
 5. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 6. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the pakistani##1
 8. the game-smoker is the fan of salsa##1
 9. the brazilian is the fan of folk##1
10. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in the middle##1
11. the fan of folk is on the right of the american##1
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is the german##1
13. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
14. the canadian is on the right of the game-smoker##1
15. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
16. the person who's hobby is traveling is the german##1
17. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the fan of indie##1
18. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
19. the malaysian is the fonseca-smoker##1
20. the tiparillo-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
