.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: january, may, october, april, september, august, november
7 different pets are kept: snake, goldfish, goat, chinchilla, mouse, hamster, bird
The people use 7 different means of transport: train, car, bus, bike, jet-ski, boat, snowmobile
House: art-deco, tower, craftsman, colonial, ranch-style, gothic-revival, november-polo
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is the owner of the goldfish##1
 2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 4. the person driving the car is the colonial house##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is the gothic-revival house##1
 6. the craftsman house is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the bus is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
10. the tower house is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the owner of the bird is the craftsman house##1
12. the owner of the goldfish is the ranch-style house##1
13. the november-polo house is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
14. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
15. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
16. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
17. the person who's birthday is in april is the craftsman house##1
18. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
19. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
20. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
21. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |      2      |      3      |       4       |     5     |    6    |    7     |
| Birthday   | october     | may    | january | november         | september   | august  | april |
| Pet       | goldfish | snake      | mouse   | goat    | chinchilla    | hamster    | bird |
| Transport      | train   | bus | snowmobile | bike | boat | car | jet-ski  |
| House      | ranch-style  | tower  | november-polo  | art-deco      | gothic-revival    | colonial | craftsman |

